#, no-wrap, priority:500
msgid "7th EC Framework Programme (FP7)"
msgstr "Settimo Framework Programme della CE (FP7)"

#. type: Content of: <activityset><activity><description>
#: fsfe.org/activities/fp7/activity.en.xml:8
#, no-wrap, priority:500
msgid ""
"     The European Commission funds research and development through official \n"
"     framework programmes (FP for short). From 2007 these framework programmes \n"
"     were used to select projects for support until 2013. The FSFE played a \n"
"     central role in supported projects related to Free Software. \n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"      La Commissione Europea finanzia ricerca e sviluppo attraverso framework\n"
"      programmes ufficiali (FP in breve). Dal 2007 questi framework\n"
"      programmes sono stati usati per selezionare i progetti a cui fornire supporto fino al 2013. La FSFE\n"
"      ha giocato un ruolo centrale nel sostenere progetti inerenti il Software Libero.\n"
"    "
